author: ekoneil
msg: Switch the NetUI webapp template off of Global.app and onto SharedFlow.jpfs.
In a new NetUI application, you'll get one with a WEB-INF/src/shared/SharedFlow.jpfs that's also wired into the default /Controller.jpf.
Update the webapp template to reflect this.
